item.title: CVE-2017-14184|2024-09-16T16:43:11.051Z -- fortinet%2C%20inc. -- forticlient%20for%20windows
item.description: An Information Disclosure vulnerability in Fortinet FortiClient for Windows 5.6.0 and below versions, FortiClient for Mac OSX 5.6.0 and below versions and FortiClient SSLVPN Client for Linux 4.4.2334 and below versions allows regular users to see each other's VPN authentication credentials due to improperly secured storage locations.
